# whitespace-only-line

## Input

```
key value
  
foo bar

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..21
  ENTRY@0..10
    WORD_KEY@0..3
      WORD@0..3 "key"
    SPACE@3..4 " "
    LINE_STRING@4..9
      STRING@4..9 "value"
    NEWLINE@9..10 "\n"
  SPACE@10..12 "  "
  NEWLINE@12..13 "\n"
  ENTRY@13..21
    WORD_KEY@13..16
      WORD@13..16 "foo"
    SPACE@16..17 " "
    LINE_STRING@17..20
      STRING@17..20 "bar"
    NEWLINE@20..21 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..3 "key",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@4..9 "value",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@13..16 "foo",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@17..20 "bar",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

